44510|title=\u72af\u7f6a\u73fe\u5834 A Witness Out of the Blue|accessdate=2020-03-31}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.imdb.com/Sections/Countries/HongKong IMDB list of Hong Kong films] \n\n{{CinemaofHongKong}}\n{{Filmsbycountry}}\n{{2019 films}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of Hong Kong films by year|2019]]\n[[Category:2019 in Hong Kong|Films]]\n[[Category:Lists of 2019 films by country or language|Hong Kong]]\n[[Category:2019 in Chinese cinema|Hong Kong]]\n", "name_user": "Quebec99", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fix duplicate ref names \u2013You can help!", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Hong_Kong_films_of_2019"}
